  <brief_title>Effects of an Oxymizer on Endurance Time in Patients With Chronic Lung Diseases</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of an Oxymizer Versus Conventional Nasal Cannula on Endurance Time in Patients With Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease IV (COPD) or Interstitial Lung Disease (ILD)</official_title>
